{
  "name": "Whitepaper & Report Summarizer",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📄 Whitepaper & Report Summarizer\n\n### How it works\n1. Watches Google Drive folder for new whitepapers/reports\n2. Downloads and extracts structured data (title, author, stats, findings)\n3. Generates AI executive summary with actionable insights\n4. Compiles and formats all extracted information\n5. Logs document metadata to Google Sheets research library\n6. Shares formatted summary to Slack channel\n\n### Setup steps\n1. Create Google Drive folder for whitepapers and reports\n2. Get PDF Vector API key from pdfvector.com/api-keys\n3. Create Google Sheet with columns:\n   Title, Author, Organization, Type, Industry, Published, Pages, Key Statistics, Findings, Recommendations, Keywords, Document Link, Added Date\n4. Connect Google Drive, Sheets, and Slack credentials\n5. Update folder ID and spreadsheet ID in nodes\n\n### Perfect for\n- Analysts processing industry reports\n- Researchers tracking publications\n- Content marketers curating insights\n- Executives needing quick document summaries",
        "height": 560,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "sticky-main",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -140,
        -96
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🎯 Extracted Data\n\n- Title and author\n- Organization\n- Document type\n- Main thesis\n- Key statistics\n- Methodology\n- Main findings\n- Conclusions\n- Recommendations\n- Data sources\n- Keywords",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 220
      },
